wiki.content: According to the Kickstarts Songfacts, Example penned this track whilst on tour when he was missing his girlfriend. He wrote it in two hours when he was travelling from Glasgow back to London. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
